  "detailed_description": "<h1>Developer Note</h1><p>Hello, I am the developer of Soulbound. And, as you may know, being the only dev has some limitations, so if happen that a bug pass my testing, please let me know and I'm more than happy to fix as soon as I can. <br><br>You can write to the support email or join in Discord here: </p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>In a place of reality, a soul longs for an escape and is not alone; matter may not be on your side, but energy is. Soulbound is an atmospheric platformer packed with action where the past is your future.<br><br>As a Metroidvania style platformer in a dark and hostile environment, that will challenge your soul. A guide system will lead your lost soul of course, you are not lost, your soul has a purpose, you just have yet to discover it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/ca65017f431259046847e8a794c72973.poster.avif?t=1618498901\" width=540 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/ca65017f431259046847e8a794c72973.webm?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/ca65017f431259046847e8a794c72973.mp4?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Back the environment to a previous state without affecting you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/30e859a8652304c11cc78c200a42c172.poster.avif?t=1618498901\" width=540 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/30e859a8652304c11cc78c200a42c172.webm?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/30e859a8652304c11cc78c200a42c172.mp4?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Back off your actions without affecting the environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/089e904b6d2cd7bc9afd4ba5d5f3f071.poster.avif?t=1618498901\" width=540 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/089e904b6d2cd7bc9afd4ba5d5f3f071.webm?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/089e904b6d2cd7bc9afd4ba5d5f3f071.mp4?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Traverse through material obstacles and use energy to jump.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore A story That Has Already Happened ...</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "In a place of reality, a soul longs for an escape and is not alone; matter may not be on your side, but energy is. Soulbound is an atmospheric platformer packed with action where the past is your future.<br><br>As a Metroidvania style platformer in a dark and hostile environment, that will challenge your soul. A guide system will lead your lost soul of course, you are not lost, your soul has a purpose, you just have yet to discover it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/ca65017f431259046847e8a794c72973.poster.avif?t=1618498901\" width=540 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/ca65017f431259046847e8a794c72973.webm?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/ca65017f431259046847e8a794c72973.mp4?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Back the environment to a previous state without affecting you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/30e859a8652304c11cc78c200a42c172.poster.avif?t=1618498901\" width=540 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/30e859a8652304c11cc78c200a42c172.webm?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274720/extras/30e859a8652304c11cc78c200a42c172.mp4?t=1618498901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Back off your actions without affecting the environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste